  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Sophisticated Dark\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Sophisticated Dark\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"flex h-[768px] w-[1024px] overflow-hidden bg-[#F5EDD8] font-sans text-[#0A0806] selection:bg-[#C9A84C] selection:text-white\\\">\\n  <style>\\n    @import url(\'https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;1,700&family=Inter:wght@400;600&display=swap\');\\n    .font-serif { font-family: \'Playfair Display\', Georgia, serif; }\\n    .font-sans { font-family: \'Inter\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; }\\n    .custom-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 4px; }\\n    .custom-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #0A0806; }\\n    .custom-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #C9A84C; }\\n    .map-grid { background-image: radial-gradient(#C9A84C 0.5px, transparent 0.5px); background-size: 24px 24px; }\\n    .topo-line { stroke: #C9A84C; stroke-width: 0.5; stroke-dasharray: 4 2; opacity: 0.3; }\\n  </style>\\n\\n  <aside class=\\\"w-[420px] h-full bg-[#0A0806] flex flex-col border-r border-[#C9A84C]/40 text-[#F5EDD8] relative z-20\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"p-8 border-b border-[#C9A84C]/20\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"text-[#C9A84C] text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-2 font-sans\\\">Progetto: Beta 1</div>\\n      <h1 class=\\\"text-4xl font-serif leading-tight\\\">Sistema Geospaziale <span class=\\\"italic text-[#C9A84C]\\\">Unicum</span></h1>\\n      <p class=\\\"mt-4 text-sm opacity-60 font-sans leading-relaxed\\\">\\n        Catalogazione scientifica e mappatura dei complessi ipogei di Napoli. Esplorazione stratigrafica dell\'acquedotto e delle necropoli.\\n      </p>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"px-8 py-6 bg-[#12100E]\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex gap-2 mb-6\\\">\\n        <button class=\\\"flex-1 py-2 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest border border-[#C9A84C] bg-[#C9A84C] text-[#0A0806] font-semibold\\\">Tutto</button>\\n        <button class=\\\"flex-1 py-2 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest border border-[#C9A84C]/40 hover:bg-[#C9A84C]/10 transition-colors\\\">Acquedotti</button>\\n        <button class=\\\"flex-1 py-2 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest border border-[#C9A84C]/40 hover:bg-[#C9A84C]/10 transition-colors\\\">Necropoli</button>\\n      </div>\\n      \\n      <div class=\\\"relative\\\">\\n        <input type=\\\"text\\\" placeholder=\\\"Cerca sito archeologico...\\\" class=\\\"w-full bg-transparent border-b border-[#C9A84C]/40 py-2 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-[#C9A84C] placeholder:text-[#F5EDD8]/30\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute right-0 top-2 opacity-40\\\">\\n          <svg width=\\\"16\\\" height=\\\"16\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\"><circle cx=\\\"11\\\" cy=\\\"11\\\" r=\\\"8\\\"/><path d=\\\"M21 21l-4.35-4.35\\\"/></svg>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto custom-scroll\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"group cursor-pointer border-b border-[#C9A84C]/10 p-6 hover:bg-[#C9A84C]/5\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[#C9A84C] text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Sito #01 - Acquedotto</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] opacity-40\\\">40.85\302\260 N / 14.25\302\260 E</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-serif\\\">Ipogeo dei Cristallini</h3>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-xs mt-2 opacity-50 line-clamp-2 leading-relaxed\\\">Complesso funerario ellenistico situato nel cuore del rione Sanit\303\240, esempio sublime di pittura greca.</p>\\n      </div>\\n      \\n      <div class=\\\"group cursor-pointer border-b border-[#C9A84C]/10 p-6 hover:bg-[#C9A84C]/5 bg-[#C9A84C]/10 border-l-2 border-l-[#C9A84C]\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[#C9A84C] text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Sito #02 - Ipogeo</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] opacity-40 text-[#C9A84C]\\\">Active</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-serif text-[#C9A84C]\\\">Buca di San Gennaro</h3>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-xs mt-2 opacity-80 line-clamp-2 leading-relaxed\\\">Cavit\303\240 strategica utilizzata come rifugio antiaereo durante il conflitto mondiale. Profondit\303\240: -40m.</p>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"group cursor-pointer border-b border-[#C9A84C]/10 p-6 hover:bg-[#C9A84C]/5 opacity-60\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[#C9A84C] text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Sito #03 - Rifugio</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] opacity-40\\\">40.84\302\260 N / 14.24\302\260 E</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-serif\\\">Galleria Borbonica</h3>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-xs mt-2 line-clamp-2 leading-relaxed\\\">Capolavoro dell\'ingegneria civile ottocentesca, via di fuga sotterranea per la monarchia.</p>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"p-4 bg-[#050403] text-[9px] text-center uppercase tracking-widest text-[#C9A84C]/40\\\">\\n      Napoli Sotterranea \302\251 2024 - Registro Archeologico Digitale\\n    </div>\\n  </aside>\\n\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col relative\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex-1 relative overflow-hidden bg-[#F5EDD8] map-grid\\\">\\n      <svg class=\\\"absolute inset-0 w-full h-full opacity-30 pointer-events-none\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 800 600\\\">\\n        <path d=\\\"M100 150 Q 200 100, 350 200 T 600 150\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"#C9A84C\\\" stroke-width=\\\"0.5\\\"/>\\n        <path d=\\\"M50 400 Q 250 350, 400 500 T 750 450\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"#C9A84C\\\" stroke-width=\\\"0.5\\\"/>\\n        <circle cx=\\\"420\\\" cy=\\\"320\\\" r=\\\"80\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"#C9A84C\\\" stroke-dasharray=\\\"2 2\\\"/>\\n      </svg>\\n      \\n      <div class=\\\"absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-4 h-4 bg-[#0A0806] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_0_8px_rgba(201,168,76,0.2)] animate-pulse\\\"></div>\\n      <div class=\\\"absolute top-[45%] left-[55%] group\\\">\\n        <svg width=\\\"24\\\" height=\\\"24\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" fill=\\\"#C9A84C\\\" class=\\\"drop-shadow-lg cursor-pointer hover:scale-110 transition-transform\\\">\\n          <path d=\\\"M12 2L4.5 20.29L5.21 21L12 18L18.79 21L19.5 20.29L12 2Z\\\"/>\\n        </svg>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"absolute top-8 right-8 flex flex-col gap-2\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-[#0A0806] p-2 border border-[#C9A84C]/40 flex flex-col gap-2 shadow-xl\\\">\\n          <button class=\\\"w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center text-[#C9A84C] hover:bg-[#C9A84C]/20 transition-colors font-bold\\\">+</button>\\n          <div class=\\\"h-px bg-[#C9A84C]/20\\\"></div>\\n          <button class=\\\"w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center text-[#C9A84C] hover:bg-[#C9A84C]/20 transition-colors font-bold\\\">-</button>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-[#0A0806] p-2 border border-[#C9A84C]/40 shadow-xl\\\">\\n          <button class=\\\"w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center text-[#C9A84C] hover:bg-[#C9A84C]/20 transition-colors\\\">\\n             <svg width=\\\"16\\\" height=\\\"16\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\"><path d=\\\"M2 12h20M12 2v20\\\"/></svg>\\n          </button>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"absolute bottom-8 right-8 flex gap-6 items-end\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 border border-[#0A0806]/10 text-[10px] font-sans\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-2 font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C]\\\"></div> Legenda Unicum\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-1 opacity-80 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2\\\"><span class=\\\"w-2 h-2 bg-[#0A0806]\\\"></span> Acqua</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2\\\"><span class=\\\"w-2 h-2 border border-[#0A0806]\\\"></span> Necropoli</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2\\\"><span class=\\\"w-2 h-2 bg-[#C9A84C]\\\"></span> Rifugio</div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"h-[240px] bg-[#F5EDD8] border-t-2 border-[#0A0806] flex relative z-10\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-[40%] p-8 border-r border-[#0A0806]/10\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\\\">\\n          <h2 class=\\\"text-3xl font-serif\\\">Buca di San Gennaro</h2>\\n          <span class=\\\"px-2 py-0.5 bg-[#0A0806] text-[#C9A84C] text-[10px] uppercase font-bold mt-1\\\">Rifugio</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex gap-4 mb-4\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex flex-col\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase opacity-50\\\">Profondit\303\240</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-sm font-sans font-bold\\\">-40.00 MT</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex flex-col\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase opacity-50\\\">Umidit\303\240</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-sm font-sans font-bold\\\">88%</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex flex-col\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase opacity-50\\\">Stato</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-sm font-sans font-bold text-[#C9A84C]\\\">ISPEZIONABILE</span>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n        <button class=\\\"mt-4 border border-[#0A0806] px-6 py-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-bold hover:bg-[#0A0806] hover:text-[#F5EDD8] transition-all\\\">\\n          Visualizza Rilievo 3D\\n        </button>\\n      </div>\\n      \\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 p-8 overflow-y-auto custom-scroll bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-[#C9A84C]/5\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"max-w-xl\\\">\\n          <h4 class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 mb-3\\\">Dossier Archeologico</h4>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#0A0806]/80 font-serif\\\">\\n            Il sito denominato \\\"Buca di San Gennaro\\\" costituisce uno dei nodi pi\303\271 critici della stratigrafia sotterranea partenopea. Originariamente scavato come cisterna greca nel IV secolo a.C., venne successivamente integrato nel sistema idrico augusteo. Durante il 1943, il sito fu adattato come ricovero collettivo per la popolazione civile, potendo ospitare fino a 400 persone simultaneamente. Le pareti conservano ancora grafiti d\'epoca e resti delle installazioni elettriche originali.\\n          </p>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </main>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Sophisticated Dark\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Sophisticated Dark\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"flex h-[768px] w-[1024px] overflow-hidden bg-[#F5EDD8] font-sans text-[#0A0806] selection:bg-[#C9A84C] selection:text-white\\\">\\n  <style>\\n    @import url(\'https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;1,700&family=Inter:wght@400;600&display=swap\');\\n    .font-serif { font-family: \'Playfair Display\', Georgia, serif; }\\n    .font-sans { font-family: \'Inter\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; }\\n    .custom-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 4px; }\\n    .custom-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #0A0806; }\\n    .custom-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #C9A84C; }\\n    .map-grid { background-image: radial-gradient(#C9A84C 0.5px, transparent 0.5px); background-size: 24px 24px; }\\n    .topo-line { stroke: #C9A84C; stroke-width: 0.5; stroke-dasharray: 4 2; opacity: 0.3; }\\n  </style>\\n\\n  <aside class=\\\"w-[420px] h-full bg-[#0A0806] flex flex-col border-r border-[#C9A84C]/40 text-[#F5EDD8] relative z-20\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"p-8 border-b border-[#C9A84C]/20\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"text-[#C9A84C] text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-2 font-sans\\\">Progetto: Beta 1</div>\\n      <h1 class=\\\"text-4xl font-serif leading-tight\\\">Sistema Geospaziale <span class=\\\"italic text-[#C9A84C]\\\">Unicum</span></h1>\\n      <p class=\\\"mt-4 text-sm opacity-60 font-sans leading-relaxed\\\">\\n        Catalogazione scientifica e mappatura dei complessi ipogei di Napoli. Esplorazione stratigrafica dell\'acquedotto e delle necropoli.\\n      </p>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"px-8 py-6 bg-[#12100E]\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex gap-2 mb-6\\\">\\n        <button class=\\\"flex-1 py-2 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest border border-[#C9A84C] bg-[#C9A84C] text-[#0A0806] font-semibold\\\">Tutto</button>\\n        <button class=\\\"flex-1 py-2 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest border border-[#C9A84C]/40 hover:bg-[#C9A84C]/10 transition-colors\\\">Acquedotti</button>\\n        <button class=\\\"flex-1 py-2 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest border border-[#C9A84C]/40 hover:bg-[#C9A84C]/10 transition-colors\\\">Necropoli</button>\\n      </div>\\n      \\n      <div class=\\\"relative\\\">\\n        <input type=\\\"text\\\" placeholder=\\\"Cerca sito archeologico...\\\" class=\\\"w-full bg-transparent border-b border-[#C9A84C]/40 py-2 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-[#C9A84C] placeholder:text-[#F5EDD8]/30\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute right-0 top-2 opacity-40\\\">\\n          <svg width=\\\"16\\\" height=\\\"16\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\"><circle cx=\\\"11\\\" cy=\\\"11\\\" r=\\\"8\\\"/><path d=\\\"M21 21l-4.35-4.35\\\"/></svg>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto custom-scroll\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"group cursor-pointer border-b border-[#C9A84C]/10 p-6 hover:bg-[#C9A84C]/5\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[#C9A84C] text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Sito #01 - Acquedotto</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] opacity-40\\\">40.85\302\260 N / 14.25\302\260 E</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-serif\\\">Ipogeo dei Cristallini</h3>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-xs mt-2 opacity-50 line-clamp-2 leading-relaxed\\\">Complesso funerario ellenistico situato nel cuore del rione Sanit\303\240, esempio sublime di pittura greca.</p>\\n      </div>\\n      \\n      <div class=\\\"group cursor-pointer border-b border-[#C9A84C]/10 p-6 hover:bg-[#C9A84C]/5 bg-[#C9A84C]/10 border-l-2 border-l-[#C9A84C]\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[#C9A84C] text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Sito #02 - Ipogeo</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] opacity-40 text-[#C9A84C]\\\">Active</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-serif text-[#C9A84C]\\\">Buca di San Gennaro</h3>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-xs mt-2 opacity-80 line-clamp-2 leading-relaxed\\\">Cavit\303\240 strategica utilizzata come rifugio antiaereo durante il conflitto mondiale. Profondit\303\240: -40m.</p>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"group cursor-pointer border-b border-[#C9A84C]/10 p-6 hover:bg-[#C9A84C]/5 opacity-60\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[#C9A84C] text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Sito #03 - Rifugio</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] opacity-40\\\">40.84\302\260 N / 14.24\302\260 E</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-serif\\\">Galleria Borbonica</h3>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-xs mt-2 line-clamp-2 leading-relaxed\\\">Capolavoro dell\'ingegneria civile ottocentesca, via di fuga sotterranea per la monarchia.</p>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"p-4 bg-[#050403] text-[9px] text-center uppercase tracking-widest text-[#C9A84C]/40\\\">\\n      Napoli Sotterranea \302\251 2024 - Registro Archeologico Digitale\\n    </div>\\n  </aside>\\n\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col relative\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex-1 relative overflow-hidden bg-[#F5EDD8] map-grid\\\">\\n      <svg class=\\\"absolute inset-0 w-full h-full opacity-30 pointer-events-none\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 800 600\\\">\\n        <path d=\\\"M100 150 Q 200 100, 350 200 T 600 150\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"#C9A84C\\\" stroke-width=\\\"0.5\\\"/>\\n        <path d=\\\"M50 400 Q 250 350, 400 500 T 750 450\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"#C9A84C\\\" stroke-width=\\\"0.5\\\"/>\\n        <circle cx=\\\"420\\\" cy=\\\"320\\\" r=\\\"80\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"#C9A84C\\\" stroke-dasharray=\\\"2 2\\\"/>\\n      </svg>\\n      \\n      <div class=\\\"absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-4 h-4 bg-[#0A0806] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_0_8px_rgba(201,168,76,0.2)] animate-pulse\\\"></div>\\n      <div class=\\\"absolute top-[45%] left-[55%] group\\\">\\n        <svg width=\\\"24\\\" height=\\\"24\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" fill=\\\"#C9A84C\\\" class=\\\"drop-shadow-lg cursor-pointer hover:scale-110 transition-transform\\\">\\n          <path d=\\\"M12 2L4.5 20.29L5.21 21L12 18L18.79 21L19.5 20.29L12 2Z\\\"/>\\n        </svg>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"absolute top-8 right-8 flex flex-col gap-2\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-[#0A0806] p-2 border border-[#C9A84C]/40 flex flex-col gap-2 shadow-xl\\\">\\n          <button class=\\\"w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center text-[#C9A84C] hover:bg-[#C9A84C]/20 transition-colors font-bold\\\">+</button>\\n          <div class=\\\"h-px bg-[#C9A84C]/20\\\"></div>\\n          <button class=\\\"w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center text-[#C9A84C] hover:bg-[#C9A84C]/20 transition-colors font-bold\\\">-</button>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-[#0A0806] p-2 border border-[#C9A84C]/40 shadow-xl\\\">\\n          <button class=\\\"w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center text-[#C9A84C] hover:bg-[#C9A84C]/20 transition-colors\\\">\\n             <svg width=\\\"16\\\" height=\\\"16\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\"><path d=\\\"M2 12h20M12 2v20\\\"/></svg>\\n          </button>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"absolute bottom-8 right-8 flex gap-6 items-end\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 border border-[#0A0806]/10 text-[10px] font-sans\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-2 font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C]\\\"></div> Legenda Unicum\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-1 opacity-80 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2\\\"><span class=\\\"w-2 h-2 bg-[#0A0806]\\\"></span> Acqua</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2\\\"><span class=\\\"w-2 h-2 border border-[#0A0806]\\\"></span> Necropoli</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2\\\"><span class=\\\"w-2 h-2 bg-[#C9A84C]\\\"></span> Rifugio</div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"h-[240px] bg-[#F5EDD8] border-t-2 border-[#0A0806] flex relative z-10\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-[40%] p-8 border-r border-[#0A0806]/10\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\\\">\\n          <h2 class=\\\"text-3xl font-serif\\\">Buca di San Gennaro</h2>\\n          <span class=\\\"px-2 py-0.5 bg-[#0A0806] text-[#C9A84C] text-[10px] uppercase font-bold mt-1\\\">Rifugio</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex gap-4 mb-4\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex flex-col\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase opacity-50\\\">Profondit\303\240</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-sm font-sans font-bold\\\">-40.00 MT</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex flex-col\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase opacity-50\\\">Umidit\303\240</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-sm font-sans font-bold\\\">88%</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex flex-col\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase opacity-50\\\">Stato</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-sm font-sans font-bold text-[#C9A84C]\\\">ISPEZIONABILE</span>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n        <button class=\\\"mt-4 border border-[#0A0806] px-6 py-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-bold hover:bg-[#0A0806] hover:text-[#F5EDD8] transition-all\\\">\\n          Visualizza Rilievo 3D\\n        </button>\\n      </div>\\n      \\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 p-8 overflow-y-auto custom-scroll bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-[#C9A84C]/5\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"max-w-xl\\\">\\n          <h4 class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 mb-3\\\">Dossier Archeologico</h4>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#0A0806]/80 font-serif\\\">\\n            Il sito denominato \\\"Buca di San Gennaro\\\" costituisce uno dei nodi pi\303\271 critici della stratigrafia sotterranea partenopea. Originariamente scavato come cisterna greca nel IV secolo a.C., venne successivamente integrato nel sistema idrico augusteo. Durante il 1943, il sito fu adattato come ricovero collettivo per la popolazione civile, potendo ospitare fino a 400 persone simultaneamente. Le pareti conservano ancora grafiti d\'epoca e resti delle installazioni elettriche originali.\\n          </p>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </main>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    }
  }
}
