e successful loading of `maplibregl` globally, addressing the critical integration for proper projection. Linking `maplibregl` into the DeckGL instance ensures map tiles back the map, synchronizing coordinates and eliminating coordinate drift when zooming and panning. This will pin icons properly. Next, I am thinking about smaller icons.\n\n\n**Refining the UI Elements**\n\nI\'ve just focused on refining the UI with smaller, elegant icons with custom crosshair/dot styles. I\'ve reduced the radius and ensured high-contrast borders and a beautiful core for these points. I also decreased the label sizes and adjusted their offsets for better map cohesion. I\'m now checking image colors for the text labels and the legend.\n\n\n"
